description: Grab & Go Kabob is proud to deliver the exotic taste of the Mediterranean and Middle East to the Walnut Creek area. Specializing in delicious, authentic Persian cuisine, this truck will have you hungry for more. Savory specialties include chicken, ground beef, turkey and tri-tip kabob.  First timers absolutely must try the ground beef and ground chicken kabobs, or any of the wraps!
name: Grab and Go Kabob
